{"tid":2086660,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大戶價格陷阱：道指 DOW JONES INDEX","createTime":"2020-06-30T11:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T06:09:50.000Z","uid":43407,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"83d9a3410d8b1917729942dd5132220241b5b45a","tid":2086660,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:03:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B6%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1%E9%81%93%E6%8C%87-dow-jones-index/2684423761839551/?av=1858365591112043&amp;eav=AfbgPGjfghuKFV5gDuy75bwDrsaCgFm4Ypm2xwnTYuQxTadqYjcBCmGTSMQu1Mnimal_CoNh26xIhc_p_QGXzktH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2F%25E5%25A1%25B5%25E7%25BF%25BC%25E7%259E%25AC%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258C%25AFk%25E6%2588%25BF%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E9%2599%25B7%25E9%2598%25B1%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%258C%2587-dow-jones-index%2F2684423761839551%2F%3Fav%3D1858365591112043%26eav%3DAfbgPGjfghuKFV5gDuy75bwDrsaCgFm4Ypm2xwnTYuQxTadqYjcBCmGTSMQu1Mnimal_CoNh26xIhc_p_QGXzktH&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=b33dd918\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B6%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1%E9%81%93%E6%8C%87-dow-jones-index/2684423761839551/?av=1858365591112043&amp;eav=AfbgPGjfghuKFV5gDuy75bwDrsaCgFm4Ypm2xwnTYuQxTadqYjcBCmGTSMQu1Mnimal_CoNh26xIhc_p_QGXzktH</a><br />\n<br />\n早前幾篇文章都主力講恆指，今日介紹一個道指的trade plan。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xNv3YnF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxNv3YnF.png&h=f2d3b979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四小時圖所見，過去兩星期道指都穩定向下走，上週五跌穿了之前的低位造了lower low，早前已沽出的交易者，很可能會將止損移至25790這個明顯的阻力之上。<br />\n<br />\n另外我們亦見到今天較早時候，當價格升近25790時再次反彈向下，證明有更多散戶在這個阻力位附近入市沽出。顯而易見，他們最有可能放止蝕的位置，也極有可能是在25790之上。因此我們可以定奪在25790上方將有相當多的平倉買單給大戶去攝獵，形成了Liquidity Zone，在這個更佳的價格區域重新入市沽出(Re-accumulation)。<br />\n<br />\n所以今天的trade plan是，若稍後時間價格重回25790之上，便可以考慮沽出道指，若價格升穿zone頂26050便止蝕離場。"},{"pid":"bebd501f739fb53af14389409d892774f5d83fba","tid":2086660,"uid":318628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"沽牛指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5873d1f6fb5e6c4cc0e9428377d6f88fedb45886","tid":2086660,"uid":149257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"會唔會太早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24377780a4829f6ff0b284b699a7d42d1012fce","tid":2086660,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5873d1f6fb5e6c4cc0e9428377d6f88fedb45886","tid":2086660,"uid":149257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"會唔會太早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:29:44.000Z","msg":"你當短炒都ok"},{"pid":"9e49efafc3a4b2982f9839540ca1ae8d66ead2e6","tid":2086660,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Emx2uEF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmx2uEF.png&h=9d315953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n放返張期指嘅圖，文章嘅圖係現貨，所有個價位係有唔同。"},{"pid":"637c3fae7683df7b937ca9bc22fc56b89ba0c463","tid":2086660,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e49efafc3a4b2982f9839540ca1ae8d66ead2e6","tid":2086660,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Emx2uEF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmx2uEF.png&h=9d315953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n放返張期指嘅圖，文章嘅圖係現貨，所有個價位係有唔同。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:46:16.000Z","msg":"放返張期指嘅圖，文章嘅圖係現貨，所<span style=\"co